item.title: My server will not go online
item.dc:creator: @ziplock ziplock
item.description:
@ziplock wrote:

Download no-ip, set up a host, and connect with that host.

[quote=“mitch-junior, post:1, topic:265529”]if you already did portfordwarding than you need to change the ip of your server so its gonna linking to your ip… how to that:

open your ‘’ client file ‘’
than open ‘’ client.java ‘’
press than CTRL + F
than search for ‘’ setserver ‘’
and place your ip in there

is this what you need ? ;)[/quote]

You don’t need to specify the server to an ip address, although you do need to go into the server class and impliment the right port.
